<b>FIRST YEAR ENROLLMENT:</b><i> April 16-June 1, 2012</i><br>
<b>REQUIREMENTS FOR FIRST YEAR ENTRANCE EXAMINATION</b><br>
1. Pay the Testing Fee (P100.00) at the Treasurer's Offices.<br>
2. Fill out the Application Form and Exam Permit and attach 2 pieces, 1x1 ID picture.<br>
3. Bring the Application Form and Exam Permit during the scheduled date of testing.<br><br>
<b>ENTRANCE EXAMINATION COVERAGE</B><BR>
The First Year Entrance Examination is a battery of test covering the following:
<ul>
<li> Mental Ability
<li> Reading and Comprehension
<li> Mathematics
<li> English Language Grammar</ul>
<br>
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp<b>FIRST YEAR REQUIREMENTS FOR ENROLLMENT</b><br><br>
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp1. Grade 6 Report Card of Form 138.<br>
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp2. Photocopy of Birth Certificate.<br>
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp3. Certificate of Good Moral Character from the Principal, Adviser or Guidance &nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbspCounselor.<br>
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp4. Four pieces 1x1 colored ID picture.<br>
&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp5.If not a Filipino Citizen, present ACR and study permit.<br><br>
